<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4>Great news!</h4>
    <p>
      You are almost done signing up for Reffo.
    </p>
    <% unless @user.uses_corporate_email? %>
      <p>
        It is generally best to use your work email address so that we can automatically validate that you are currently working for a company. It will also allow you to vote and comment on offers from your company specificly.
      </p>
    <% end %>
    <p>
      In order to verify your account, please <a href="<%= verify_url @user.verification_token, email: @user.email %>">visit this link<a/>.
      <br/>
      <p style="color:#ddd;">
        If the link doesn't work, you can copy/paste the following link in your browser:
        <%= verify_url @user.verification_token, email: @user.email %>
      </p>
    </p>

    <p>Thanks, team reffo</p>
  </body>
</html>
